	renumber the useful variables so that they can be shared between SCCs.
	* src/tgbatest/sccsimpl.test, src/tgbatest/ltl2ta.test: Adjust test
	cases.

2013-04-09  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

