	* src/tgbaalgos/ltl2tgba_fm.cc (ratexp_to_dfa::translate,
	ltl_to_tgba_fm): Do not convert labels as Boolean formulas before
	creating transitions.  Use the bdd directly, and register the used
	transitions later.

